al/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"無😢"},{"pid":"b4a12c474d2edd8da553b6b0f5ddee914005357a","tid":2172600,"uid":367224,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"P(n):n^3-n+3<br />\nP(n+1):(n+1)^3-(n+1)+3<br />\n=n^3+3n^2+3n+1-n-1+3<br />\n=n^3+3n^2+2n+3<br />\n=(n^3-n+3)+3(n^2+n)"},{"pid":"6db62137ed910356ce8d69c65a097f4e04bf5fbe","tid":2172600,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2595%25B0%25E5%25AD%25A6%25E5%25BD%2592%25E7%25BA%25B3%25E6%25B3%2595&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=43b388a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n<br />\nMathematical Induction"},{"pid":"3300ddd9915f76818a85c965c8f8a047452da352","tid":2172600,"uid":267945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61564d0c5bbde2ac2a677edd760f7ba88f458916","tid":2172600,"uid":208625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZmnr8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZmnr8c.png&h=81b5ee79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解😢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"你要proof (k+1)^3-(k+1)+3 可以除得盡3"},{"pid":"9fd96ae9fc15bb22da8fb92421dc475c1d6b27d1","tid":2172600,"uid":65716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61564d0c5bbde2ac2a677edd760f7ba88f458916","tid":2172600,"uid":208625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZmnr8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZmnr8c.png&h=81b5ee79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解😢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"Google都唔識？<br />\n<a href=\"https://math.stackexchange.com/questions/1467789/prove-by-induction-that-n3-n3-is-divisible-by-3-for-all-natural-numbers-n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmath.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F1467789%2Fprove-by-induction-that-n3-n3-is-divisible-by-3-for-all-natural-numbers-n&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=d345ab72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://math.stackexchange.com/questions/1467789/prove-by-induction-that-n3-n3-is-divisible-by-3-for-all-natural-numbers-n</a>"},{"pid":"4e7f9894198085cce30b09203624ca56f286e9c0","tid":2172600,"uid":133652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"提一提 DSE out c<br />\n不過學埋冇壞"},{"pid":"44592dc96722d47adc3bc3d7983621d321665fe5","tid":2172600,"uid":243380,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"唔MI既話<br />\nn^3-n+3<br />\n= n(n+1)(n-1) +3<br />\n前面個term一定是但一個係multilple of 3<br />\n後面係係3<br />\nSo it must be divisible by 3<br />\nQED"},{"pid":"8cfb79ac141f31f5c57f0536beaeba675a5814f4","tid":2172600,"uid":210074,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"61564d0c5bbde2ac2a677edd760f7ba88f458916","tid":2172600,"uid":208625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZmnr8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZmnr8c.png&h=81b5ee79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解😢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"Let P(n) be the statement<br />\n<br />\nWhen n=1,<br />\n(1)^3-(1)+3<br />\n=3<br />\nThus P(1) is true<br />\n<br />\nAssume P(k) is true for some positive integer k.<br />\nWhen n=k+1<br />\n(k+1)^3-(k+1)+3<br />\n=k^3+3k^2+3k+1-k-1+3<br />\n=k^3+3k^2+2k+3<br />\n=(k^3-k+3)+3k^2+3k<br />\nThus P(k+1) is true<br />\n<br />\nBy the principle of Mathematical Induction, P(n) is true for all positive integers n"},{"pid":"150859e2ef444665fb1d1d0742ff066a197d4602","tid":2172600,"uid":367224,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"44592dc96722d47adc3bc3d7983621d321665fe5","tid":2172600,"uid":243380,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"唔MI既話<br />\nn^3-n+3<br />\n= n(n+1)(n-1) +3<br />\n前面個term一定是但一個係multilple of 3<br />\n後面係係3<br />\nSo it must be divisible by 3<br />\nQED"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢題用MI係牛刀嚟 不過做吓冇壞"},{"pid":"fa21a1ee0a664e5eddc336bf15f387f41b3124ce","tid":2172600,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:32:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6595215dde4e415a77f627906d15ad22314e184","tid":2172600,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"567da92a63d753a65b31d219141bb76afa3da750","tid":2172600,"uid":236413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"記得M2冇考被n整除嘅MI"},{"pid":"2e4bd1bcd72e3f04b1596603c932acdc471e1ab1","tid":2172600,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"讀開英文，見中文有啲唔慣<br />\nAssume n=1 true<br />\nLet n=k<br />\nWhen f(n+1)"},{"pid":"2316d4b4bcaf7eefb08e31cd7f6184e724d91ad2","tid":2172600,"uid":126961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91fc6ed7e49e93ff6787097a99a5995d5f473c2b","tid":2172600,"uid":344625,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:18:11.000Z","msg":"有冇英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0