2+n)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港中學數學MI要let呢樣let嗰樣好多廢話好累贅"},{"pid":"7c55a2f8602f598e1ba10914b49137f9bfe63a56","tid":2172600,"uid":107201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7f9894198085cce30b09203624ca56f286e9c0","tid":2172600,"uid":133652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"提一提 DSE out c<br />\n不過學埋冇壞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:24:58.000Z","msg":"下？<br />\n咁而家m2仲有咩淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d660454ea5ad0b3f5894ad891b532eb68100e3f","tid":2172600,"uid":198743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:25:43.000Z","msg":"M2 cut咗之後少咗好多野玩"},{"pid":"c7455a4b929d6d687aab2db6d2cba36f084edc3b","tid":2172600,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"mi都cut?<br />\nm1,m2 成科cut埋佢算啦..."},{"pid":"60373e9126e20318120261b8d58a53f033d467a4","tid":2172600,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港中學教育真係得啖笑<br />\n理科科目cut到體無完膚<br />\n然後就搞埋啲無撚用嘅stem..."},{"pid":"19f2b11590e629a6a4b92dd2dcfa08f5b469b32d","tid":2172600,"uid":89064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"let p(n) be the statement &quot; n&sup3;-n+3= 3a&quot; ,where a is integer.<br />\n<br />\nfor n=1, LHS=1-1+3 = 3 = 3(1) = RHS<br />\nso p(1)  is true<br />\nfor n=2, LHS=2&sup3;-2+3 = 9 = 3(3) = RHS<br />\nso p(2) is true<br />\n<br />\nassume that for any positive integer k, p(k)  is true.<br />\ni.e. k&sup3;-k+3=3a  <span class=\"red\">(做n=k+1果陣，要砌到有呢舊野出黎) </span><br />\n<br />\nBesides, <br />\nfor n=k+1,<br />\nLHS<br />\n=(k+1)&sup3;-(k+1) +3<br />\n=k&sup3;+3k&sup2;+3k+1-k-1+3<br />\n=<span class=\"red\">k&sup3;-k+3</span> + 3k&sup2;+3k<br />\n=<span class=\"red\">3a</span> +3k&sup2;+3k<br />\n=3a+3(k&sup2;+k)<br />\n=3(a+k&sup2;+k)<br />\n=RHS<br />\nso p(k+1) is also true.<br />\n<br />\nfinally, we can conclude that p(n)  is true."},{"pid":"80ab30e7c797e11ebd7c2e3b8014c173558d8c63","tid":2172600,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d660454ea5ad0b3f5894ad891b532eb68100e3f","tid":2172600,"uid":198743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:25:43.000Z","msg":"M2 cut咗之後少咗好多野玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:40:28.000Z","msg":"amath同pure math果種係咁堆砌d equation先最過隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb07950aa8b5a88b30db564f8a591888a75e7e3","tid":2172600,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2d7e5686ea7a83e2040c5fdcb1589659056838","tid":2172600,"uid":364074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10fad9cb00b2147507c0a0876d30c21804a94055","tid":2172600,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61564d0c5bbde2ac2a677edd760f7ba88f458916","tid":2172600,"uid":208625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZmnr8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZmnr8c.png&h=81b5ee79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解😢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"數學歸納法原理係<br />\nprove左n =1,2 correct之後，assume n=k correct先。<br />\n跟住再prove n=k+1 都係correct既話，咁就可以證明n對於所有正整數係岩，即係果句statement係岩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 解倒同表達左個logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學倒野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces